text: Sławomir Napłoszek (born 29 July 1968) is a Polish archer. Napłoszek competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 2020 Summer Olympics.Sławomir Napłoszek == References == Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Polish archers Category:Olympians for Poland Category:Sportspeople from Warsaw
